CustomField.description: The unique ending (including "__c" for custom fields) of the target Merge Result field in which the value from the involved record should be stored. This is used to derive the appropriate `EffectiveMasterRecord`, `MasterRecord` and `MergedRecord` fields.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The unique ending (including "__c" for custom fields) of the target Merge Result field
CustomField.label: Result Field Ending
